# Commit Style

Use this format when committing changes (e.g. via `agent-commit-push`, `worktree-pr`, or manual commits).

## Message Format

```
${emoji} ${type}(${scope}): ${summary}

- ${change_detail_1}
- ${change_detail_2}
```

